<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَبُو عَليّ النَّيْسَابُورِي.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٢٧٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> يُونُس بن حبيب بن<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عبد القاهر الإصبهاني.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي دَاوُد , وَالْحُسَيْن بن حَفْص<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَغَيرهمَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أخبرنَا عبد الرَّحْمَن بن يحيى , ثَنَا أَبُو بشر<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يُونُس بن حبيب.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١٢٧١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> إِسْحَاق بن شاهين<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الوَاسِطِيّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> خَالِد بن عبد الله.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>كناه مُحَمَّد ابْن إِسْحَاق بن خُزَيْمَة , فِيمَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>حَدثنِي عَنهُ أَبُو عَليّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٢٧٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> إِسْمَاعِيل بن عبد الله بن<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَسْعُود سمويه الإصبهاني.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أهل الشَّام , ومصر.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أخبرنَا مُحَمَّد بن عمر بن حَفْص , ثَنَا أَبُو بشر<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>إِسْمَاعِيل بن عبد الله بن مَسْعُود.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١٢٧٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> إِبْرَاهِيم بن نَاصح.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>الإصبهاني.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مَتْرُوك.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> النَّضر بن شُمَيْل.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">ثَنَا عَنهُ:</span> مُحَمَّد بن عمر.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>١٢٧٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> الْفُقيْمِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>مَجْهُول.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> إِبْرَاهِيم بن أدهم.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مُؤَمل بن إهَاب.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>١٢٧٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> مُحَمَّد بن عمرَان بن<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>الْجُنَيْد الدشتكي , الرَّازِيّ.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو عَليّ الْحُسَيْن بن عَليّ.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>١٢٧٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بشر:</span> أَحْمد بن مُحَمَّد بن<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>مُصعب الْمروزِي.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عَليّ بن خشرم وَغَيره<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>بموضوعات.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن كنيته أَبُو بَحر)</span><a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>١٢٧٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَحر:</span> الْأَحْنَف بن قيس.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>أدْرك النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم وَلم يره ,<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">ودعا لَهُ النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم فَقَالَ:</span><a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِر للأحنف.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>كناه عبد الْعَزِيز بن قرير.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>١٢٧٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَحر:</span> ثَعْلَبَة بن الحكم ,<span class="c5"> وَيُقَال:</span><a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>ابْن مَالك.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>أدْرك النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب بن يُوسُف ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span>سَمِعت عَبَّاس الدوري يذكر عَن ابْن معِين ,<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> ثَعْلَبَة أَبُو بَحر أدْرك النَّبِي<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>